data.name: AS_3TECN127_Audiencia
data.queryText:
SELECT t1.*
FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/73ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/73ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t1
LEFT JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/74ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/74ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t2 ON t1.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC = T2.ContactKey
LEFT JOIN {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/72ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/72ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t3 ON t1.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC = t3.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC
WHERE t2.ContactKey IS NULL
AND t3.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC IS NULL

data.name: AS_3TECN127_GC
data.queryText:
SELECT 
       tmp.CO_CLIENTE_SFMC AS 'ContactKey',
       'AS_3TECN127_Email _Supertecnoprecios_20231213' AS 'JourneyId',
       'AS_3TECN127_Email _Supertecnoprecios_20231213' AS 'JourneyVersionId',
       'AS_3TECN127_Email _Supertecnoprecios_20231213' AS 'JourneyName',
       '3TECN127' AS 'CodObjetivo',
       GetDate() AS 'Timestamp'
FROM (
    SELECT t1.*
    FROM {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/73ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/73ae7561-63a5-ee11-b85a-48df37deb0f3/data/name}}] t1
  WHERE t1.NA_RANKING = 0
  
) tmp
  /*ORDER BY NEWID()*/
